      "instruction": "<p>Take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your<strong> tomato[es] </strong>into bite-sized pieces</p>",
