    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> chicken stock mix</strong>, <strong>tomato paste </strong>and a pinch of<strong> sugar </strong>in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your<strong> tomato stock</strong></p>",
