      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>tomato stock</strong>,<strong> chopped tomato</strong> and a pinch of<strong> pepper </strong>to the pan and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Reduce the heat to medium and cook for 6-8 min or until the sauce has thickened and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Once done, remove the pan from the heat and stir through your <strong>natural</strong> <strong>yoghurt</strong></p><p>Mix until fully combined – this is your <strong>classic chicken curry</strong></p>",
